Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:11.48,flashback,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,If the heroes are fighting each other
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.82,0:00:14.49,flashback,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,instead of the Waves of Catastrophe,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.49,0:00:17.24,flashback,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,then for the sake of the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.91,0:00:19.62,flashback,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,I must kill the Four Cardinal Heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.83,0:00:23.79,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,"Kill the Four Cardinal Heroes," eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.58,0:00:25.79,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.04,0:00:27.46,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.63,0:00:30.96,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.80,0:00:37.18,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,They've really taken to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.18,0:00:38.76,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.64,0:00:48.56,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Liberation: Wind Prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.24,0:00:54.36,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Melty!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.53,0:00:58.20,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.20,0:01:04.20,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing to Mel-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.04,0:01:06.00,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Mel-tan,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.00,0:01:08.79,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,I need you to be my hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.44,0:01:30.27,sign_3370_33_The_Rising_of_th,Title Card,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,1)}The Rising of the Shield Hero
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.09,0:02:42.51,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,"Hostage"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.22,0:02:46.93,sign_5367_37_Lullaby_at_Dawn,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(486,768)}A Promise Made
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.51,0:02:44.10,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:46.93,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Shield Hero, promise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.43,0:02:50.23,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Promise me you'll make up \Nwith the other heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:52.48,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Let Mel-chan out of there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:54.19,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,And if I don't,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.19,0:02:56.40,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,you're threatening to hurt Melty?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.65,0:03:00.74,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I told you it wasn't happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.74,0:03:04.33,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Even still, I must ask you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.83,0:03:07.49,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so obsessed with \Nthe heroes working together?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.83,0:03:12.29,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Because I made a promise \Nto the hero who raised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.29,0:03:15.63,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,And because the heroes {\i1}must{\i0} cooperate
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:19.26,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,in order to save the world from the Waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.59,0:03:20.72,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:22.76,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter how many times you ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.34,0:03:25.72,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of \Nreconciling with those morons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.06,0:03:30.77,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, new heroes \Nwill have to be summoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.77,0:03:34.94,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,And to enable that, I'll kill \Nall the current heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.02,0:03:39.53,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what you meant last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.94,0:03:42.32,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,That will help the world in the long run.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:46.87,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, doing that would be easy for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.74,0:03:50.50,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Please reconcile with the other heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.67,0:03:54.08,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Even then,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:56.63,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:04:00.09,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to take Melty hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:02.88,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to kill me, feel free.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.80,0:04:04.72,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:05.81,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:06.31,top,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.76,0:04:09.77,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Just know that I'm not going \Ndown without a fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.73,0:04:12.64,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:16.69,sign_7873_50_Detecting_transf,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(318,1)}Detecting transformation jamming
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.31,0:04:18.48,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:21.19,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,I understand how you feel, Shield Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:22.15,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.99,0:04:26.78,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,If that's how it is, prove to me that
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.78,0:04:31.12,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,you and your party can \Nfight the Waves alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:32.71,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Prove to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:34.21,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,How do we do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:36.63,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,By fighting you right here and now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:40.71,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Shield Hero, I more or less \Nknow how strong you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.84,0:04:45.13,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,I want a one-on-one with Filo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:47.18,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:51.68,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,If you prove to me that you're strong,\N I'll release Mel-tan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.47,0:04:55.94,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,And I won't kill the heroes for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:57.44,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:03.69,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really understand, but if \NI win, Master won't be killed,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.69,0:05:05.95,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,and Mel-chan will be freed too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:06.41,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.41,0:05:07.45,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on, Filo—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:08.99,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:11.99,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fight in this form,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.99,0:05:15.00,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,so you fight me in human form too, Filo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.37,0:05:17.50,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.50,0:05:19.21,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I said wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:22.13,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.06,0:05:35.73,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.73,0:05:36.98,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever you're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.69,0:05:46.49,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,You're slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:53.74,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.20,0:05:55.66,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Filo! Above you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.83,0:06:02.00,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Filo-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:06.26,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:13.10,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Why did Fitoria choose to fight \NFilo and not Raphtalia?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:16.43,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,And why are they fighting in human form?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:18.94,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.94,0:06:19.98,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Filo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.98,0:06:21.86,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just charge in blindly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.23,0:06:23.82,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Use your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.57,0:06:26.19,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.82,0:06:29.03,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,And regenerate your clothes \Nwhen you have the chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.41,0:06:32.41,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Pour your mana into it and increase \Nyour defense as much as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.45,0:06:36.75,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:40.50,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,As source of your powers, Filo orders you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:42.29,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Decipher the laws of nature
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:46.01,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,and blow my target away with \Na vicious vacuum burst.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.92,0:06:49.51,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Zweit Tornado!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:53.76,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Nullify the vacuum burst.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.30,0:06:56.35,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Anti-Zweit Tornado!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:01.77,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out! It's jamming magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.73,0:07:04.90,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,You're wide open.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.49,0:07:15.45,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,She has no time to regenerate \Nher clothes at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:21.46,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Melty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:24.42,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Filo's in trouble if this keeps up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.25,0:07:27.92,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try to get rid of \Nthis cage with my shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.35,0:07:36.18,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:37.31,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:42.56,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,She cut through the shield's \Ndefense with ease!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:44.02,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:45.73,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Eyes on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.03,0:07:52.74,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,He got what he deserved for trying \Nto cheat and rescue Mel-tan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:56.33,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,But do you know why he did that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.33,0:07:57.87,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:03.42,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,What do you fight for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.42,0:08:05.92,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.92,0:08:08.84,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,For Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.84,0:08:12.59,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't beat the dragon last night,\N you can't beat me now,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.59,0:08:15.68,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,and you expect to be useful \Nto the Shield Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:17.64,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:20.56,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become strong for Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.89,0:08:23.31,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Not with such a shallow will!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:34.41,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Naofumi-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.41,0:08:36.37,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.37,0:08:39.58,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let Master get hurt any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:41.25,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I'll... I'll be much, much stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.00,0:08:45.17,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I'll... I'll be much, much stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:46.67,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.09,0:08:55.30,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,What is she...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.71,0:08:58.60,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Is she absorbing the mana \Nparticles in the air?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.30,0:09:01.72,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Is that even possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:04.48,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Filo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.48,0:09:07.10,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:08.86,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.44,0:09:12.82,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, and watch her attacks closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:15.24,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I know you can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.49,0:09:19.24,flashback,SH,0000,0000,0000,,I know you can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.08,0:09:22.08,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.88,0:09:29.00,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Too slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.67,0:09:32.17,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, but I'll still beat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:37.63,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Spiral...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.63,0:09:41.56,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:49.15,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:50.19,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Filo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:07.71,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.12,0:10:10.54,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see that magic \Nattack Filo just used?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:11.42,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.59,0:10:16.80,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:21.85,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:29.44,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Master, I'll grow stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.15,0:10:33.61,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Strong enough to protect you, Mel-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.61,0:10:35.78,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,and Raphtalia-oneechan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:40.41,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Strong enough to protect everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:43.16,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.28,0:10:45.37,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.37,0:10:49.29,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:53.25,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, Filo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:55.55,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,You win.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:10:59.80,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,I'll free Mel-tan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:01.93,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,You did well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:04.10,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Filo-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.10,0:11:12.35,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Mel-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.32,0:11:15.86,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:18.49,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I won.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.03,0:11:19.86,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.57,0:11:22.11,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You did amazing, Filo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.88,0:11:35.21,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,You did well to pass the trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:39.34,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Filo, you were being tested.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:41.59,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.97,0:11:45.64,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,If you hadn't passed it, you would've died.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:47.93,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,And the Shield Hero would have, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.10,0:11:53.81,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.81,0:11:57.57,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,A symbol proving that you overcame my trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.03,0:11:59.57,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Lower your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.53,0:12:10.04,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Filo, I appoint you my successor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.41,0:12:11.91,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Successor?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.54,0:12:17.38,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You mean she'll become \Nthe next filolial queen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:19.30,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing, Filo-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.51,0:12:28.47,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the symbol of being next in line?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.47,0:12:30.43,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a cowlick!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.43,0:12:32.18,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,C-Cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.94,0:12:35.06,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Something weird grew on my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.06,0:12:36.52,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Get it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.69,0:12:42.24,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,It grew back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.95,0:12:46.16,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,And it'll keep growing back,\Nso get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:49.49,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,And you'll gain more of them as you grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.49,0:12:51.70,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Am I gonna look like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.25,0:12:56.38,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Her stats have increased.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.38,0:12:59.67,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Does that cowlick increase her \Nbase numbers across the board?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:03.84,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Since Filo's level is capped right now,\Nthis is perfect for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:06.34,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,I also have something for you, Shield Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.34,0:13:07.22,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:08.97,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want a cowlick!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.97,0:13:10.01,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,What's a cowlick?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.01,0:13:11.89,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,It's something better.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:13.77,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,I'll heal your wounds, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.69,0:13:21.65,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Now show me your shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.19,0:13:23.28,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.91,0:13:32.41,sign_7873_50_Detecting_transf,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(313,101)}Shields were force unlocked
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.58,0:13:32.33,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Force unlocked?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.16,0:13:36.00,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,I can't use many of them because \Nmy level's not high enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.42,0:13:39.63,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,but it looks like the entire \NFilolial Series has been unlocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:42.34,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Now I just have to meet their requirements.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:44.63,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Well, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.63,0:13:46.22,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:50.26,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,But I still have something I wish \Nto discuss with you in private.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.26,0:13:51.89,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,There's more?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.89,0:13:53.56,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:14:01.52,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't use us just to \Ntest Filo-chan, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:04.94,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,I did. I feel bad for what I did to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.36,0:14:07.28,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything you desire?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:08.28,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.28,0:14:11.49,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.49,0:14:12.95,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.25,0:14:26.76,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, amazing! I'm so high up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.22,0:14:30.72,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm living the dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.72,0:14:33.14,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Is a ride really all she wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.18,0:14:36.68,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna be really big soon, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.89,0:14:41.15,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows how many cowlicks \Nyou'll have by then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.15,0:14:43.69,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:50.49,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,That was so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.49,0:14:53.33,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,The day has only just begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.33,0:14:55.79,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Get some more rest before you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.33,0:14:58.54,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:03.34,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if Fitoria's offering, why not accept?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.34,0:15:04.55,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.55,0:15:06.42,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,This is a celebration, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.42,0:15:09.00,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,We need to show you some \Nreal hospitality as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:15.47,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,A party to celebrate the \Nappointment of a new queen?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.47,0:15:16.89,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,You mean me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.89,0:15:18.98,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go making decisions for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:20.98,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Filo-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.19,0:15:28.11,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Me too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.16,0:16:23.25,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Picking up where you left \Noff this afternoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.92,0:16:26.50,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really try to make up with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:27.84,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Not this again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:31.05,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Did you try to clear your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:34.26,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.85,0:16:50.86,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I didn't bother, \Nthinking they'd never believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.82,0:16:57.16,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't tell them they're wrong, \Nyou're basically admitting your guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:16:58.58,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.03,0:17:02.41,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to drop you off close
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:05.67,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,to another hero when I take you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:07.17,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You're coming with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.58,0:17:10.05,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,I won't involve myself any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.63,0:17:13.88,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Show me you four are worthy \Nof my involvement.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:18.14,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to talk it out \Nright then and there, right? Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:21.22,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.02,0:17:23.43,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:24.98,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,No, there's more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.31,0:17:28.56,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,If even one Cardinal Hero is \Nmissing when a Wave hits,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:31.03,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,fighting it off will be \Nexponentially more difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:36.86,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,If that looks likely, it's better to \Nkill you all and summon new heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.24,0:17:41.20,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,So if all four of us don't \Ntalk it out and reconcile,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:43.91,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,you'll kill us anyway, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.84,0:17:54.05,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell you after how \Nmany Waves it will happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.05,0:17:57.76,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,but there will come a time when the \Nworld demands sacrifices from all life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:18:00.35,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,The world will demand sacrifices?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.72,0:18:05.27,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,The heroes will be forced to choose \Nwhat they fight for in that battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:08.15,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,I'm waiting for that time to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.44,0:18:09.98,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Choose what we fight for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.27,0:18:13.86,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Will you fight for the world, \Nor will you fight for its people?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:18.66,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,If you choose the world, \Nmany lives will be lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.78,0:18:23.12,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,But you'll be able to fulfill your duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.79,0:18:26.46,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,And what if we choose the people?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.54,0:18:29.33,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a thorny path.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.13,0:18:33.21,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,How much do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.96,0:18:36.92,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,There is a lot I have forgotten,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.92,0:18:39.64,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,but there is one thing I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.64,0:18:43.22,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Saving the world isn't the \Nsame as saving its people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:48.48,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Past heroes wished for their \Nsuccessors to save the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.48,0:18:53.07,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I get it, but it makes sense for \Nheroes of the people to choose them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.07,0:18:54.90,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do it as you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.19,0:18:59.07,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,You can't overcome all \Nthose hurdles by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.45,0:19:03.62,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you telling me all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.91,0:19:07.83,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't it be easier to \Nconvince another hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:16.55,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,I rate you higher than the other heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.55,0:19:17.38,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.80,0:19:21.51,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,You raised Filo, the next queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.51,0:19:23.10,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't possibly be a bad guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.05,0:19:25.89,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I am a bad guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.89,0:19:28.06,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,If you say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.56,0:19:31.10,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,I believe you have it in you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.10,0:19:35.15,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,to talk it out with the other heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:38.82,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you four heroes are far too weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.19,0:19:43.78,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I don't kill you personally, \Nyou'll die sooner rather than later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.24,0:19:47.29,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Are the upcoming battles \Ngoing to be that rough?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.87,0:19:51.71,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll need the Rage Shield\N more than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:55.84,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,If you absolutely must use that shield...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.55,0:20:01.76,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.93,0:20:05.72,sign_32007_288_Barbarian_Armor_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(112,1)}Barbarian Armor +1
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.72,0:20:08.43,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,That will slow down the \NCurse Shield's corrosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:12.31,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,But it won't completely stop it,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.31,0:20:14.23,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,so try to avoid using it as much as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.61,0:20:17.40,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,After all that talk about killing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.40,0:20:20.06,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're just really nice, Fitoria.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:23.95,flashback,SH,0000,0000,0000,,You're really nice,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:25.37,flashback,SH,0000,0000,0000,,Fitoria.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.91,0:20:34.92,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Well, given you're doing all this for me,\NI guess I'll give it my best shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.92,0:20:36.63,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,But don't get your hopes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.09,0:20:40.51,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Could you get off?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.38,0:20:45.43,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Shield Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.30,0:20:51.68,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, was it the Shield Hero who raised you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:53.56,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.56,0:20:55.77,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Filolials have short memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.82,0:20:59.90,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.86,0:21:07.74,italics,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,But I remember this gentle touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.40,0:22:52.73,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,This is the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.62,0:23:00.88,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Here's where the Four Cardinal Weapons'...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.88,0:23:03.44,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. There's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.83,0:23:13.49,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.96,0:23:15.49,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,It's empty!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.51,0:23:19.69,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.69,0:23:21.09,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.22,0:23:39.97,sign_81788_789_Walking_Over_Cor,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(356,1)}A Conspiracy Linked
